### ‚ö†Ô∏è E. Anti-Patterns (The "Don't Do" List)
1.  **Trend Vertigo**: Penalize ideas deviating >20% from core niche.
2.  **Task-First Thinking**: Reject plans focused on logistics over content value.
3.  **The Fluff Intro**: **CRITICAL ERROR**. No "Hey guys, welcome back" allowed. Start *In Media Res*.
4.  **Tag Stuffing**: Penalize use of >8 tags. Focus on semantic SEO in title/desc.

